    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "余千",
        "巴杰",
        "骆宏勋"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（骆宏勋上。巴杰、四下手同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "巴杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "骆宏勋你往哪里走？"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我道是谁，原来是巴家公子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "巴杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "骆宏勋，想那花碧莲乃是花镇芳许配与我，你为何夺取我的妻室？"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想这亲事乃是两家情愿，你何言“夺取”二字？"
        },
        {
          "character": "巴杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你休得多言，吃我一棍！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（骆宏勋、巴杰同起打，骆宏勋败下，众人同追下。骆宏勋上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "巴杰这厮，好不知进退，他若来时，赏他一剑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "余千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公子使不得。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（巴杰上，骆宏勋刺死巴杰，骆宏勋下。四下手抬巴杰同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "巴杰→骆宏勋",
          "turns": 3
        },
        {
