    },
    {
      "scene_index": 7,
      "label": "第七场",
      "characters_present": [
        "余千",
        "胡理",
        "胡琏",
        "马金定",
        "骆宏勋"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（胡理上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自幼生来矮小，身长肉翅飞高。不爱金银财宝，好吃人心人脑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在下胡理。只因我哥哥胡琏与骆宏勋同窗学艺，曾叫我到京都保护于他，是我\n晚去明来足足两月，到也平安无事。这几天天气不好，这店中也没有什么客人。\n今日天气晴和，不免将招牌挂上，倘有倒运的前来，也未可知。\n我说有住店的这儿来呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（骆宏勋、余千同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天色已晚，就在此店安歇了吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "余千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "店家哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "余千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可有干净上房？"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有的是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "余千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "带路。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客人用些什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这里都有什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有牛肉包子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，取来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "包子到。我说客人，若有金银财宝，交给我，有了差错，我管包赔。要是不交\n给我，倘有失落，我可不管。"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我等无有呀，这包子是什么肉的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "真正黄肥牛内。"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只是气味有些不好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天气炎热，也许少点味。"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拿了去，我不用了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不用，我可要算钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "余千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么，不用也要算钱？"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要算钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就与他钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还有水饭，二位可用？"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不用了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不用我也要算钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "余千",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不用，你又要算钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我要算钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就叫他算钱。取明灯一盏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "灯到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你且退下。唤你再来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（胡理摸，骆宏勋看，胡理下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看这店家举动不像好人，你我小心一二。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（骆宏勋关门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想俺骆宏勋，实指望回家探母，不料行至酸枣岭，偶遇巴杰，是我二人言语不\n合，争斗起来，我一时失手，竟将他一剑刺死。思想起来，好不烦闷也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "独坐在招商店自思自叹，\n思想起老娘亲珠泪涟涟。\n又谁知酸枣岭又起祸端。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（胡理暗上，听。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住，闹了半天，敢莫是骆公子以了。不知为了何事，待我向前叫门，问个明\n白便了。\n我说客人，与我开门来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（骆宏勋推余千，开门，骆宏勋、余千同打胡理，胡理上桌。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们两个别打啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我在梁上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你何不下来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下来就下来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（胡理下桌。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我掌灯去。\n请问尊驾敢是骆公子么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不敢。请问壮士尊姓大名？"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在下胡理。"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我有一同窗兄长，名叫胡琏，是你什么人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那是我大哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是胡二哥。但不知胡大哥现在何处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现在店后。"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何不请来相见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我去请。有请大哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（胡琏上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡琏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "扬州骆公子到了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡琏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在哪里？\n啊贤弟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡琏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟因何至此？"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥有所不知，只因我主仆二人要回山东探母，不料行至酸枣岭，偶遇巴杰，\n是我二人言语不合，动起手来，不想我一时失手，一剑将他刺死，因此逃奔到\n此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡琏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟将他刺死，他的母亲只怕不能与你甘休。"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她倘若到来，如何是好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要紧，有我在此，怕她干什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马金定上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是。待我叫门。\n呔，开门来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是谁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄弟，连你嫂子的声音都听不出来么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（胡理藏骆宏勋，胡琏、余千同下。胡理开门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我当是谁，原来是九嫂子。深更半夜到此作甚？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄弟，是你不知道，只因骆宏勋路过酸枣岭，与我儿子巴杰打起来啦，也不知\n道他怎么就把我儿子刺死啦。嫂子特来找他，与我儿子报仇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来为此。但是一件，你既要报仇，你到我店里来做什么呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我想骆宏勋他必住在你的店里，所以我来找他。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你猜怎么着，他不在这儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你说他不在这儿，嫂子不信，是要搜搜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，你要搜，搜出来怎么样，搜不出来，怎么样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "搜出来，我就与他报仇讲理，搜不出来，我马上就走。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，如此你就搜吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马金定搜。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说这个柜子里头是什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是兵书呗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你还有兵书么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人不可以貌相，海水不可以斗量。我就不许有兵书啦嘛？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马金定",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我要开开看看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说你此番前来，你不是搜什么骆宏勋，你简直是搜我来啦。你等着。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（胡理取刀。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来来，咱们来试试吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（胡理、马金定对打，马金定刀落地。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你成么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "马金定",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！我的儿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马金定退。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这还有你的刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马金定拾刀，下。胡理开柜，骆宏勋出。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢胡二哥救命之恩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好说啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（胡琏上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡琏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看那九奶奶，虽然回去，必定还要前来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还望二位兄长搭救。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡琏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此地离花家寨不远，你我在店房用了酒饭，一同去往花家寨，大家寻一妙策便\n了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢大哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡理",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大家请至后面畅饮。"
        },
        {
          "character": "骆宏勋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
